Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this ever-changing world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where should we float off to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,   286 VIEWS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn off the AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to sing music\Nthat was made for Vocaloid, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Tomo-chan, I feel like\Nyou're better at writing music,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so don't you think we should find a\Nvocalist who can do it justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to make do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget I said anything. Let's keep making\Nmusic together as we always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really... think we should give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,22,738 FOLLOWERS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're really serious\Nabout chasing our dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}AIM FOR THE BUDOKAN!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}6: Hymn of the Outcasts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how's your throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A... bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bwit bwetter?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru, come to the sauna.\NYou too Nina, it'll help with the throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, you can't keep losing\Nyour voice every time you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No pain, no gain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all part of the experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ouch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that was one hell of a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And Nina just went wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you didn't get carried away too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And she's Drum Player-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello, I'm Player!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I can't use my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to make up a character.\NI'm the high school cutie, Play-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... leaving first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, she's totally hooked now, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- You mean Nina?\N- Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mo-mo-ka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to read the\Ncomments from our concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"DD really isn't the same without Momoka-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"It was definitely more authentic\NRock than whatever DD's producing now."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, they're even calling\Nyou cute Nina, isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My point is, all customers agree\Nthe old DD was way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, call them out\Npublicly that they're all frauds now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That we're the real deal,\Nso people should follow us instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen how many followers DD has?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,200k...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And counting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And how many do {\i1}we{\i0} have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,500...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you suggest we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep practicing whenever we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Make music. Throw concerts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's our goal as a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking what {\i1}your{\i0} goal is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just took a bath to relax,\Nleave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanna know too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be a pro, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit weird
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone like you to team up\Nwith a pair of amateurs like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes one wonder what you're really after.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got no goals?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. None.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,God, she pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck, fuck, fuck, fuck!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it with the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime you try to have a conversation,\Nshe's always, always, ALWAYS...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're so aggressive about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a bull beefing with a bullfighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Beef... Gyudon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's never gonna open up\Nif you don't give her some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to make her feel\Ncomfortable enough to open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you need to be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being honest here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... I wonder what\Nshe's really feeling right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka aside, what is it that\N{\i1}you{\i0} want for the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To triumph over Diamond Dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the lofty dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pros with a company\Nbacking them, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Band Goals"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"How to become a pro band"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- You want to go pro?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What, did you get an offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that, it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, back in the day you were\Nhoping to be scouted at performances,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sending a demo reel,\Ngoing to auditions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But these days, it's the bands that\Nhit it big on the net that get scouted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that big of a deal to get signed to a label?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays you can self-publish online, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it a lot harder to get\Ncollabs, promos, and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, you should try matching\Nwhat DD reached on their own back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls built up 10k followers\Nwhile in their hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when a label noticed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's all about the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Each follower is a potential attendee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The bigger the number,\Nthe better the chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}471 FOLLOWERS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It... went down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,   
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,   
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,   
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'd rather nothing change than risk losing anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'd rather nothing change than get hurt."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's a bad idea to let go of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you do, just please take off those stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa... do you think it'll work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the best of friends can end up arguing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And even the most toxic relationships\Ncan somehow work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I see those three...\NI feel like you'll fit right in, Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna practice a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should call it a day\Nso we can wrap up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You cool with that, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, would it be okay to take some time\Nto brainstorm the outfits for our next show?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You picked them last time too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We could go with something\Nslightly cuter this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh by the way, do you mind if I upload\Nthe pics I took of you earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ooh, nice stuff!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dazzling!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're gonna rake in the followers--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought since you seemed so into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Post {\i1}your{\i0} own mug then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I just thought that... uh, our fans\Nwould be grateful and appreciative?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if my grandma sees it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that desperate for followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to cultivate an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's maximize the marketing\Nby dressing up as schoolgirls
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and rename ourselves to "Shin Kawasaki School Idol Club".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're too old, wouldn't that count as fraud--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let a woman dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I mean, if that gets us more followers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. You'd be no different than\Nthe current Diamond Dust then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll be difficult to reach\Ntheir level if we don't go pro
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do that we need to build more fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did we agree on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if we don't,\Nwe're gonna lose to Diamond Dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, since when have we been competing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no beef with DD, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drag the whole band into your petty daydreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so... I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look Nina, I get how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know, but...\N- Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the sudden obsession for going pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I think going pro\Nwill solve all our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think we can beat\NDiamond Dust even if we go pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I don't wanna give up without even trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't think we're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Medium without the onions, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A medium, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. Two mediums--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the team!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're musicians?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Rupa. And she's Ebizuka Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been making music for a while,\Njust the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this rings a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a pretty popular hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:13:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize you\Nsince you didn't show your faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so the reason you reached out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna do a rock battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Murder?\N- Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, I know! We're your store's 10,000th custom--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're slow on the uptake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're scouting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Like, for the army?\N- Not that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,WE. WANT. TO. SCOUT. YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Scout?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Scout who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you want us to do sexua--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we want to make music\Nwith the three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- No way.\N- Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to your show the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the two of us\Ntalked it out and agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That we want to give this\Na shot with you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No wayyyy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sellout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But... we don't really have an established audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor many fans or followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We could say the same about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the same then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, we got an offer from a label once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we started negotiating with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We felt they weren't really thinking\Nabout what we truly wanted out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, they only care if it sells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to put it bluntly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say it wasn't\Nwhat we were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So where do we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. When we saw your concert, we felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you're the types who only\Nsing what {\i1}you{\i0} want to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought you'd share our vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, that's exactly why I sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Nina {\i1}loves{\i0} sharing visions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go ahead.\N- Thank you for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a second\Nwhile I turn on the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go touching anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow, a lizard!\N- It's called a {\i1}gecko{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aim for the Budokan", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Budokan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,S-so what? What's wrong with dreaming a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! If anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even dreamed of something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So is the Budokan like a big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What, haven't you heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's a really important venue from TV, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan, you're from Sendai though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sendai, Kagoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Kumamoto next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? She meant {\i1}the{\i0} Sendai, Miyagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you came this far,\Nwanna go see it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, do we have to go at {\i1}this{\i0} hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now now, I think it's important\Nthey see it with their own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,BUDOKAN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If we sing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we sing here, maybe we could\Nprove we weren't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That we aren't losing to Diamond Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,AIM FOR THE BUDOKAAAAAN!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me call Momoka-san ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you a dumbass or what?\N- What's wrong now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san said we needed\Na bassist and keyboardist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But to dream of the Budokan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same as going pro.\NYou think Momoka-san will just agree with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are you saying we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you think of anything else,\Nyou self-righteous freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like we have any other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise you won't call me a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you if you promise me you won't call me a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's well mixed and well paced too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And they play the bass and the keyboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could try collabing for a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}they{\i0} think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cool! Even more, they wanna--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, they offered to\Npractice together this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You free?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me know later so I can confirm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Liar!\N- I call it strategizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like she's not against {\i1}not{\i0} not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just my impression, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like there are two Momokas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that when it comes to music,\Nshe pours her heart into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To make the best music she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who wants her music to leave an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it's not about the music itself,\Nshe comes back down to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already given up on the industry once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So she likely wonders if there's any point\Nin trying seriously again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she in or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can show her we can make\Na proper band, she might change her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a musician at heart after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta practice already? What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Practice now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be a good girl and follow my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,SOME DAYS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A proper studio is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's something up with this cable...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Detective Granny{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, this photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan's such a big fan\Nshe's seen the series three times over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always bawling her eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you're lucky to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Awa Tendo is known for not\Ninteracting much with fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... {\i1}Awa{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You called?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- I demand an explanation.\N- 'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Rupa, the bassist. Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's Tomo-chan, our keyboardist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... you're from the gyudon place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your continued patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Order something other than a\Nmedium and a beer, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to meet you,\NI'm Kawaragi the guitarrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary Kawaragi Momoka\Nof Diamond Dust fame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not done talking, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are we playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the song\Nfrom our last concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cool, but will these\Ntwo be able to play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we rehearsed a bit before you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll spice it up a little bit though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that okay?\N- Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know how it'll\Ncome out 'till we try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One, two, three, four.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow... what is this? Oh my...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This city flows down a whirlpool of truths{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where should we float off to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this ever changing world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should we raise up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, we actually wanted to ask\Nif these two could join our band.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your music won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Music festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first step should be\Nto make a big impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got a division for amateurs as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If our application gets picked,\Nwe get a big stage and a lot of eyes on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And hope a big label notices us then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:21:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A festival is the biggest gathering\Nof music talent there is, so,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's a prime location for scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To find the {\i1}diamond{\i0} in the rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be playing...
